{"tid":1611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［痴撚線］九龍城 6個月大B女被搶走","createTime":"2016-11-25T16:41:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-25T17:01:23.000Z","uid":8700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d4c79120f790bf1ac31c4b9e852689e37165e0d6","tid":1611,"uid":8700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T16:41:36.000Z","msg":"6個月大B女在九龍城被抱走逾3小時，女嬰母親急召男友人來幫忙，與警員分頭行事，四處尋找B女下落。男友人向記者透露，B女當時身穿粉紅色BB衫，相信被一對年約30餘歲內地男女搶走。<br />\n<br />\n附近食肆職員稱，由於正值周末黃金時段，未有留意外面情況，但發現大批警員忙於奔走，有別往常。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20131123/51930036\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20131123%2F51930036&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=27eff33d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20131123%2F51930036&h=a66a0dab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20131123/51930036</a>"},{"pid":"afeb681e367de064abaf23f638fa5d5795e290b9","tid":1611,"uid":3297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T16:59:55.000Z","msg":"捉到留低一隻手先講"},{"pid":"31481199cb8593bf86be4f2343947b44e7b56bcb","tid":1611,"uid":5637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:01:23.000Z","msg":"2013年11月23日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}